LECOMTE v. LANGIER. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. December 15, 1893.) Action by Rene J. Lecomte against Jeanne Claire Angele Langier, epouseeOde, sued as Angele Ode Langier.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and FOLLETT and PARKER, JJ.

G. H. Brewster, for plaintiff. Carter, Hughes & Kellogg, for defendant.

No opinion. Motion dismissed.
